{"tid":778021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關愛座，關你老母咩","createTime":"2018-08-13T11:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T11:30:35.000Z","uid":22927,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1acebb54d83c6b4f2875723a3e35e5fda5f23e5e","tid":778021,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"會讓就讓，唔讓就唔讓嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n整埋d 關愛座增加社會矛盾，on99<br />\n以前無關愛座無人讓座咩？<br />\n整左又個個讓咩？<br />\n見你有需要咪讓囉，<br />\n覺得你無需要咪唔讓囉，<br />\n邊有得逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔舒服咪call 白車囉，<br />\n咁唔掂咪搭的士囉，<br />\n又唔掂，又唔call 白車，<br />\n又無錢搭的士咪求人比個位你囉，<br />\n你啤我做乜鳩啫，你啤我就知你諗乜撚呀？<br />\n仲有呀，你求我我都唔係一定要讓比你㗎，<br />\n唔撚係奉旨㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96f46dc2d64676fc712909c5fd4de72090efa33","tid":778021,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:26:10.000Z","msg":"其實土共真係好識分化<br />\n以前就收買班廢老，搞到後生冇晒機會上位<br />\n好喇，而家仇老風氣重，班老野真係自食其果"},{"pid":"2271a9801498b83f3088a7131e5db647e9614dbb","tid":778021,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"睇人黎讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39c801ebd819d7a6e1a50072ba2bdca915a7172","tid":778021,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"整關愛座之前：<br />\n讓座=好人 +1分<br />\n唔讓座=無嘢 0分<br />\n<br />\n整關愛座之後：<br />\n讓座=應份 0分<br />\n唔讓座=賤人 -1分<br />\n<br />\n同一個動作，由好事變壞事，on9"},{"pid":"77302b158ef766824f5c1276be405bfab76dd718","tid":778021,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"以為講緊關sir<br />\n出返去先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/034143_856a78b314be230abb82e11d560a1dbd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%